// PHOTON ENGINE - MESH PROCESSING AND OPTIMIZATION UTILITIES
// =============================================================================
// Comprehensive mesh processing tools including simplification, optimization,
// LOD generation, mesh generation, analysis, and GPU-accelerated operations.
// Based on Harper Engine WP-186-210 mesh processing papers.
